          "_name": "features16",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"features15\" group=\"Features\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"1\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"1\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"imageWidth\" title=\"Image\" min=\"4\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Card Color\" name=\"cardColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background3.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#98dee8\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"content-wrapper\">\n            <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\n                <div class=\"col-12 col-lg\">\n                    <div class=\"text-wrapper\">\n                        <h6 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><b>Acerca de nuestro trabajo</b></h6>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">Cada producto que elaboramos refleja la calidad de nuestro trabajo y la pasión que ponemos en cada impresión.<br>No solo ofrecemos artículos, sino soluciones creativas que comunican, inspiran y permanecen.<br><br>Nuestra línea de productos combina materiales de primera calidad, técnicas de impresión avanzadas y una atención cuidadosa a los detalles.<br>El resultado: acabados duraderos, colores vibrantes y diseños fieles a tu estilo o marca.<br></p>\n                        <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\"><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Learn more</a></div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-{{imageWidth}}\">\n                    <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                        <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/gymdesign-1160x1121.jpg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\">\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
